I"U<h1 id="time-and-cost-reporting">Time and cost reporting</h1>

<p>You can easily report spent time and costs in OpenProject and filter, group and save the reports according to your needs.</p>

<div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
**Note**: To use the time tracking functionality, the **Time and costs module** needs to be activated in the [project settings](../../projects/project-settings/modules/).
</div>

